\begin{verbatim}
Dataset15
\end{verbatim}
A struct containing UFF Dataset 15 metadata.

\textbf{Fields}

\begin{itemize}
\item \texttt{type::Symbol}: Data set type


\item \texttt{node\_ID::Vector\{Int\}}: Node label


\item \texttt{def\_cs\_num::Vector\{Int\}}: Definition coordinate system number


\item \texttt{disp\_cs\_num::Vector\{Int\}}: Displacement coordinate system number


\item \texttt{color::Vector\{Int\}}: Color


\item \texttt{coords::Vector\{Vector\{Float64\}\}}: 3D coordinates of node in the definition system

\end{itemize}
